metadata.name: Space Blazer #1
metadata.description: Space Blazers is a community driven collection of 3333 stylistically curated 3D NFTs orbiting around the Ethereum blockchain. Your Space Blazers doubles as your SB membership token, and grants access to members-only benefits like community giveaway, raffles, exclusive airdrops and more. Using ERC-721A for cheap $GAS. Visit spaceblazers.io for more details!
